snippet.title: 3D PEN CAN FIX YOUR LIFE || 36 REUSE AND RECYCLE CRAFTS AND DIYs || DIY Helicopter And BBQ Grill
snippet.description:
Repurposing ideas, repair crafts, and incredible DIY decorations you’ll love

Do you also love crafting and decorating? Then you’ve come to the right place. Today I show you some brilliant DIY crafts you can try at home. Let’s start with 3D pens. Those little powerful handheld tools will help you add some flare to your next big project or fix something broken. 

For example, using a watermelon halve, you can create a hat. 

Have you ever broken your favorite coffee mug? Then, instead of chucking it away, use your 3D pen to fix it. Just make sure you fill the area with multiple coarse layers that go in different directions to ensure no liquid will seep through.  

If you’re looking for more challenging projects. I show you how to turn a steel drum into a fully functional BBQ grill. You can also take an old chair from the trash and restore it into beautiful furniture. Or, take a soda can, an old helicopter toy, and re-design it from scratch. 

Timestamps: 
0:45 – How to fix a broken coffee mug with a 3D pen
3:16 – How to fix a hole in a screen mesh
3:48 – Making a BBQ grill from scratch

11:46 – An inspiring helicopter project
14:50 – Cool DIYs using cardboard boxes

snippet.title: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता का उल्टा चश्मा | Episode 555 | 29th September, 2020
snippet.description:
Subscribe to Sony Pal: http://www.youtube.com/sonypalindia

Episode 555: Jethalal Intoxicated With Bhaang
-----------------------------------------
Taarak is stressed as Jethalal is intoxicated and tries to confess his love for Babita. Taarak decides to lock him up in his house and leave for shiv yatra. Daya decides to stay back till Jethalal comes.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
-------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble for all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

snippet.title: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता का उल्टा चश्मा | Episode 556 | 29th September, 2020
snippet.description:
Subscribe to Sony Pal: http://www.youtube.com/sonypalindia

Episode 556: Everyone Looks For Jethalal
-----------------------------------------
Everyone assumes Jethalal to be kidnapped as he's gone for a long time. Taarak asks the doctor about how to minimize the effect of Bhaang. Jethalal realized how he consumed sweets which turned out to be intoxicated.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
-------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble for all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

snippet.title: Writer Fighter Hua - Sit-down Comedy by Varun Grover
snippet.description:
Wrote and performed this standup bit for the first edition of SWA Awards 2020 organised by the official body that represents all the lyricists and writers of Indian film industry - The Screenwriters Association. 

First standup video shot completely at home since this lockdown began. Bada mushkil hai ghar pe comedy karna. Aadmi bewakoof lagta hai hawa mein joke sunaate huye. But maybe ab yahi future hai. I mean 'bewakoof lagna.' 

Shot by: Raj Kumari 
Edited by: Abhishek Bhutwani 
Sound by: Sreejith Menon 
Created for: Screenwriters Association (SWA) 
Title inspired by: Jaspal Bhatti's Flop Show's title song

snippet.title: Minecraft Live: Vote for the Moobloom!
snippet.description: Which mob do you want to see in Minecraft? Vote for the Moobloom if you feel like flowers and cows living as separate entities has gone on long enough! It’s time to combine them and luckily for us it turned out adorable. Please don’t ask about the Meowtree, sometimes the question isn’t ”can we” but ”should we, because the branches have claws, oh no the branches ARE claws”. In any case, if you are on Team Moobloom head over to Minecraft Live on October 3rd to cast your vote! Read more about the mob vote here: https://minecraft.net/article/minecraft-live-vote-for-next-mob

snippet.title: ITS A.... !?! ARE WE HAVING A BOY OR A GIRL?!?
snippet.description:
Hey guys! Today we are finding out what we are having (eeeek!) we filmed this 10 weeks ago, and just wanted to keep it to ourselves for a while before we shared with the world. We're having a....?!!!! 

The disbelief is more or less that in this entire 2 day span with having the 20 week ultrasound, and getting the results of the baby, that it really made real the reality of being parents. We KNEW it was real, but we hadn't seen the baby since 8 weeks, so this (being we saw the baby, how much the baby had grown etc) and the NEXT DAY found out what we were having, that is my shock and disbelief. How real it all is, and just picturing what our life will be like from here on out. We are SO EXCITED and cannot handle it!! bursting with love 

Enjoy!

snippet.title: Skip & Shannon react to LeBron's Lakers vs. Miami Heat in the 2020 NBA Finals | NBA | UNDISPUTED
snippet.description:
The Los Angeles Lakers handled business and closed out their series against the Denver Nuggets on Saturday to advance to the Finals for the first time since 2010. LeBron James made sure the series wouldn’t be going 6 games by putting up a 38-point triple-double. The Miami Heat, who closed out the Boston Celtics last night, are now all that stand in the way of LeBron winning his first title as a Laker. Hear what Skip Bayless and Shannon Sharpe have to say about the upcoming series between the Lakers and Heat.

In this video we'll review why Adesanya's leg kicks were so effective in beating Costa, plus, what could possibly be going on with the MMA star's chest?

Israel Adesanya defeated Paulo Costa at UFC 253 to retain the middleweight championship belt and he did it in part thanks to nearly perfect lower leg kicks. But also, what's the deal with his chest looking so strange during the fight? In this video we'll review why Adesanya's leg kicks were so effective in beating Costa, plus, what could possibly be going on with the MMA star's chest? 

UPDATE: I was off on the point about unilateral vs bilateral as many have pointed out in the comments. I appreciate the feedback and everyone pointing this out and will always admit if I missed something. In this case i was quick to defend an athlete I saw being accused unfairly of steroid use and didnt do enough research on a topic outside of my expertise. lesson learned, will keep working to be better.

snippet.title: SEC Shorts - LSU tries to play off that Mississippi State loss
snippet.description: Well that's one way to announce your arrival in the Southeastern Conference.  Mike Leach and the Mississippi State Bulldogs strolled into Death Valley and walked out with a major upset win of the defending national champions.  While many were counting the Bulldogs out before the season began, Leach showed just how potent his pass happy Air Raid offense can be against...well anyone.

snippet.title: Chris Broussard talks Lakers on to NBA Finals after series win, LeBron mindset | FIRST THINGS FIRST
snippet.description:
Chris Broussard joins the show & reacts to the Los Angeles Lakers advancing to the NBA Finals after their conference finals series win against the Denver Nuggets. Broussard thinks LeBron James was helpful in getting the Lakers to the finals but didn't do it alone. He also feels if the Lakers don't win a championship, it would be one of the biggest upsets in NBA history.

snippet.title: Minecraft Live: Vote for the Moobloom!
snippet.description: Which mob do you want to see in Minecraft? Vote for the Moobloom if you feel like flowers and cows living as separate entities has gone on long enough! It’s time to combine them and luckily for us it turned out adorable. Please don’t ask about the Meowtree, sometimes the question isn’t ”can we” but ”should we, because the branches have claws, oh no the branches ARE claws”. In any case, if you are on Team Moobloom head over to Minecraft Live on October 3rd to cast your vote! Read more about the mob vote here: https://minecraft.net/article/minecraft-live-vote-for-next-mob

snippet.description:
Thanks to fuboTV for sponsoring this video! 
Go to http://fubotv.com/brianmd to start your FREE trial and get 15% off your first month.

Israel Adesanya defeated Paulo Costa at UFC 253 to retain the middleweight championship belt and he did it in part thanks to nearly perfect lower leg kicks. But also, what's the deal with his chest looking so strange during the fight? In this video we'll review why Adesanya's leg kicks were so effective in beating Costa, plus, what could possibly be going on with the MMA star's chest? 

UPDATE: I was off on the point about unilateral vs bilateral as many have pointed out in the comments. I appreciate the feedback and everyone pointing this out and will always admit if I missed something. In this case i was quick to defend an athlete I saw being accused unfairly of steroid use and didnt do enough research on a topic outside of my expertise. lesson learned, will keep working to be better.

localizations.en.description:
Thanks to fuboTV for sponsoring this video! 
Go to http://fubotv.com/brianmd to start your FREE trial and get 15% off your first month.

Israel Adesanya defeated Paulo Costa at UFC 253 to retain the middleweight championship belt and he did it in part thanks to nearly perfect lower leg kicks. But also, what's the deal with his chest looking so strange during the fight? In this video we'll review why Adesanya's leg kicks were so effective in beating Costa, plus, what could possibly be going on with the MMA star's chest? 

UPDATE: I was off on the point about unilateral vs bilateral as many have pointed out in the comments. I appreciate the feedback and everyone pointing this out and will always admit if I missed something. In this case i was quick to defend an athlete I saw being accused unfairly of steroid use and didnt do enough research on a topic outside of my expertise. lesson learned, will keep working to be better.

More UFC Videos!
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLrdpldKEF236khwdFNRilNeOZded9gZLD

Follow Me on Twitter!
https://twitter.com/b_sutterer

I'm a doctor and a sports fan and this channel is dedicated to exploring the unique medical side of the world of sports, including NBA, MLB, NFL, UFC, and many more! Breaking down the biggest what ifs, historical injuries and stories, and making learning about medicine fun and relevant for all sports fans!

Anatomy images: www.biodigital.com

DISCLAIMER: Content not intended to be taken as medical advice. Opinions are my own and do not represent those of my employer. I have not personally treated or evaluated the individual(s) discussed in this video. Content used with educational and transformative intent within Fair Use Guidelines
Content owned and produced by Brian Sutterer LLC 2020

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Liverpool vs Arsenal (3-1) | Premier League
snippet.description:
Our winning start to the season is over after Liverpool fought back to beat us at Anfield.
 
A bizarre goal from Alex Lacazette saw us lead the champions and lay the foundations for a memorable result. But our advantage lasted just two minutes as Sadio Mane and Andy Robertson struck to turn the tide in Liverpool's favour.

Diogo Jota then put the game to bed moments before full time with a crisp finish into the bottom left-hand corner. 

#arsenal #highlights #premierleague

For more match action, highlights and training videos, make sure you become a digital member and sign up to Arsenal Player. It's FREE and is the Home of the Game: https://arsn.al/arsenalplayer

This is the Official YouTube channel for Arsenal Football Club. This channel will aim to showcase the personality of Arsenal Football Club and give fans more of an insight into what it's like to be at this fantastic club. This channel will look behind the scenes and get closer to the likes of Mesut Ozil, Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang, David Luiz, Nicolas Pepe, Alexandre Lacazette, Mesut Ozil, Bernd Leno, Granit Xhaka, Hector Bellerin, Bukayo Saka, Gabriel Martinelli, Bukayo and more.

ABOUT ARSENAL FC


Arsenal Football Club were formed in 1886. They have amassed 13 League titles, 14 FA Cups and many other major trophies since then. Their greatest players include: Thierry Henry, Dennis Bergkamp, Tony Adams, Ian Wright, Robert Pires, Liam Brady, Patrick Vieira, Cliff Bastin and Charlie George.

snippet.title: BTS: Tiny Desk (Home) Concert
snippet.description:
For new music, the latest Tiny Desk (home) concerts and more, sign up for the NPR Music newsletter, sent weekly: npr.org/nprmusicnewsletter

Sept. 21, 2020 | Stephen Thompson -- We've been trying to make a BTS Tiny Desk concert happen for years now — even gaming out ways we might move Bob Boilen's desk far enough forward to accommodate the superstar Korean boy band's dance moves.

In the end, it took a global pandemic — and the launch of Tiny Desk (home) concerts back in March — to make something happen. With BTS cooped up in Seoul, the group held true to the series's spirit by convening a live band for its Tiny Desk debut, and even arranged to perform in a workspace with a music-friendly backdrop: the record store VINYL & PLASTIC by Hyundai Card in BTS's hometown.

Opening with this summer's inescapable "Dynamite" — the group's first single to hit No. 1 in the U.S., as well as its first song to be fully recorded in English — BTS leaned hard into the new track's celebratory, "Uptown Funk"-adjacent vibes. From there, the group dipped into its back catalog, seizing on the opportunity to showcase its quieter side while (mostly) staying uncharacteristically seated. The breezily propulsive "Save ME," from 2016, ultimately gave way to a full-on power ballad in 2017's reflective "Spring Day."

The latter track seemed especially true to BTS's hopeful nature: Introduced with a few optimistic words from rapper and singer RM ("It's been the roughest summer ever, but we know that spring will come"), the song reflects on a need to wait out hard times, even as the weight of present-day pain feels oppressive.

BTS had intended to spend 2020 delighting the BTS Army in arenas around the world, only to spend these last few months performing in isolation. Released on the last day of a grim season, "Spring Day" provides a nice reminder of what awaits us on the other side. We just have to get through fall and winter first.

SET LIST
"Dynamite"
"Save ME"
"Spring Day"

MUSICIANS
V: vocals; Jin: vocals; Jimin: vocals; J-Hope: vocals; RM: vocals; SUGA: vocals; Jungkook: vocals; KHAN: drums; DOCSKIM: keyboard; Kim Kiwook: bass; Shyun: guitar

CREDITS
Video and Audio by: Big Hit Entertainment; Producer: Stephen Thompson; Audio Mastering Engineer: Josh Rogosin; Video Producer: Morgan Noelle Smith; Associate Producer: Bobby Carter; Executive Producer: Lauren Onkey; Senior VP, Programming: Anya Grundmann


ABOUT THE SERIES

The Tiny Desk is working from home for the foreseeable future. Introducing NPR Music's Tiny Desk (home) concerts, bringing you performances from across the country and the world. It's the same spirit — stripped-down sets, an intimate setting — just a different space.

snippet.title: 黃鴻升 Alien Huang 柯有倫 Alan Kuo 竇智孔 Bobby Dou 【扛得住 Carry On】Official Music Video
snippet.description:
【ROCK HDMV】
歡迎訂閱滾石唱片YouTube官方頻道 → http://bit.ly/RockRecords
#黃鴻升 #柯有倫 #竇智孔  《#扛得住》MV

Alien留給地球的最後一首友情歌
願大家一起將正能量傳出去

Alien黃鴻升「Plan B 專輯」第5首單曲
《扛得住》
黃鴻升 X 柯有倫 X 竇智孔
三位好友合唱
為後疫情時代的我們加油打氣
兄弟陪你一定可以扛得住

ALIEN黃鴻升2020專輯「Plan B」，從2019年開始籌備製作，這張專輯從最開始的A&R到專輯概念、企劃文案、拍攝ＭＶ，黃鴻升不假手他人，全部自己一手包辦，經紀人曾經擔心他手上工作太多太忙，在他寫歌詞卡關的時候，跟他說要不要乾脆找人寫詞，他思考了幾秒，肯定地說，他可以的，他自己來！

2019年6月陸續推出《蒸發》、《人生定番》、《Plan B》，時隔多月，在2020年6月再推出《我不是空笑夢》，在忙碌於主持節目、廣告代言、戲劇之外，黃鴻升對於歌手身份，已不想要只是做一個被公司規劃好的「歌手」，而是希望透過自己親手創作歌詞、寫歌曲介紹文案、拍攝ＭＶ，為自己的音樂找定位，為自己想唱的歌創造生命。

這首《扛得住》，預定在2020年9月底上架，在9月13日釋出歌名與三人的宣傳照，只是，來不及讓大家讀到他為這首歌寫的介紹文字。
所以，延續「Plan B」的精神，催生這首歌的柯有倫，以及共同合唱的竇智孔，各自為好友黃鴻升、為三人合唱的這首歌，寫下一段話，希望能夠真切傳達，關於這首歌的誕生、靈感與精神。

Alan柯有倫：
這首歌的誕生，最大的原因，其實是因爲今年疫情的關係，看到大家生活上面都遇到一些比較大的困苦，所以想要鼓勵大家，在這段時間一定要扛得住。

我們有個高爾夫球群組，前一陣子三個人常一起去高爾夫球練習場練球，因爲我們三個都希望，從今年開始，即使再忙，我們三個人都可以保持每一個月一定要下場打一場高爾夫球。
有一天，因爲這首歌寫出來，我就傳到群組裡面給他們聽，我說有沒有機會跟兩位兄弟一起唱這首歌。當然，他們兩個一聽完之後，立刻答應。
後來，我們去錄音室錄完這首歌的時候，鴻升跟我說，他希望可以把這首歌放在他的全新專輯，我跟竇哥聽了之後，當然也是一口答應。

這首歌詞曲創作的靈感，就像當年的《笨小孩》，我一直希望可以做一首是像當年的笨小孩，有三個兄弟，用一首曲子表達一種正面的力量。
我們三個人的想法應該都是一樣的，就是希望在生命裏面很簡單，然後可以做一件事情，是讓我們三個人都覺得是很正面，然後很快樂的。
在這個打拼的路上，我們三個兄弟互相都看到彼此的辛苦，也看到彼此的堅持與執着。希望能用這種心境，去鼓勵所有不管是遇到困難、或者是遇到挫折的人。

想跟鴻升說的就是，這一趟太短了，下輩子我們再做朋友、我們再做兄弟，有你在身邊一起並肩作戰，是我這一輩子最驕傲最光榮的事。

竇智孔：
9月18日.晚上18:42分
在收到滾石發來的信息後，
我想這是你搞的鬼吧！
我崩潰了。
你..太賤了....
我會在我的隱形筆記本裡註記的。
然後，
我回頭翻著簡訊，
我找到了我們兄弟情開始的地方。
我承認我不是一個好相處的人。
但你的舉動讓我決定把牆全打開了。
簡訊裡
我：我們外景提來賓，不知道你會不會願意來幫忙。
你：只要你需要我的，我就盡全力幫忙，ok!（你就是這麼可愛）
我想緣分就是這麼簡單
然後，我們完成了一些回憶，
當然我們還有很多約好的計畫……

沒事，兄弟，再見。
兄弟我扛得住！
我們保持聯絡⋯。

⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯

『無論是逼不得已，或是因為是退卻而放棄、
無論如何，儘管緊緊擁抱遺憾，時間仍舊不可逆。
時針分針秒針，前進的頻率不同， 方向卻總是一致。
時針不會為了你而開始逆轉，但你可以順著時間的流，釐清造成的不甘的源頭，
毫無懸念的繼續順時針前行。』

—截自Alien黃鴻升，2019/11/28 寫於「Plan B」專輯概念

計劃趕不上變化、時間也無法倒轉，
面對遺憾和困難，請讓 扛得住 成為定番。

這是他留給地球的最後一首友情歌，只要有音樂陪伴，相信大家一定扛得住；願每個人都永遠記得鴻升帶來的美好，一起將他的正能量傳遞出去。

黃鴻升 柯有倫 竇智孔《扛得住》♫ https://RockRecordsCo.lnk.to/CarryOn

扛得住 Carry On
演唱 Performed by：黃鴻升 Alien Huang / 柯有倫 Alan Kuo / 竇智孔 Bobby Dou
作曲 Composer：王君蒲 Apollo Wang
作詞 Lyricist：王君蒲 Apollo Wang

(黃)

snippet.localized.title: 黃鴻升 Alien Huang 柯有倫 Alan Kuo 竇智孔 Bobby Dou 【扛得住 Carry On】Official Music Video
snippet.localized.description:
【ROCK HDMV】
歡迎訂閱滾石唱片YouTube官方頻道 → http://bit.ly/RockRecords
#黃鴻升 #柯有倫 #竇智孔  《#扛得住》MV

Alien留給地球的最後一首友情歌
願大家一起將正能量傳出去

Alien黃鴻升「Plan B 專輯」第5首單曲
《扛得住》
黃鴻升 X 柯有倫 X 竇智孔
三位好友合唱
為後疫情時代的我們加油打氣
兄弟陪你一定可以扛得住

ALIEN黃鴻升2020專輯「Plan B」，從2019年開始籌備製作，這張專輯從最開始的A&R到專輯概念、企劃文案、拍攝ＭＶ，黃鴻升不假手他人，全部自己一手包辦，經紀人曾經擔心他手上工作太多太忙，在他寫歌詞卡關的時候，跟他說要不要乾脆找人寫詞，他思考了幾秒，肯定地說，他可以的，他自己來！

2019年6月陸續推出《蒸發》、《人生定番》、《Plan B》，時隔多月，在2020年6月再推出《我不是空笑夢》，在忙碌於主持節目、廣告代言、戲劇之外，黃鴻升對於歌手身份，已不想要只是做一個被公司規劃好的「歌手」，而是希望透過自己親手創作歌詞、寫歌曲介紹文案、拍攝ＭＶ，為自己的音樂找定位，為自己想唱的歌創造生命。

這首《扛得住》，預定在2020年9月底上架，在9月13日釋出歌名與三人的宣傳照，只是，來不及讓大家讀到他為這首歌寫的介紹文字。
所以，延續「Plan B」的精神，催生這首歌的柯有倫，以及共同合唱的竇智孔，各自為好友黃鴻升、為三人合唱的這首歌，寫下一段話，希望能夠真切傳達，關於這首歌的誕生、靈感與精神。

Alan柯有倫：
這首歌的誕生，最大的原因，其實是因爲今年疫情的關係，看到大家生活上面都遇到一些比較大的困苦，所以想要鼓勵大家，在這段時間一定要扛得住。

我們有個高爾夫球群組，前一陣子三個人常一起去高爾夫球練習場練球，因爲我們三個都希望，從今年開始，即使再忙，我們三個人都可以保持每一個月一定要下場打一場高爾夫球。
有一天，因爲這首歌寫出來，我就傳到群組裡面給他們聽，我說有沒有機會跟兩位兄弟一起唱這首歌。當然，他們兩個一聽完之後，立刻答應。
後來，我們去錄音室錄完這首歌的時候，鴻升跟我說，他希望可以把這首歌放在他的全新專輯，我跟竇哥聽了之後，當然也是一口答應。

這首歌詞曲創作的靈感，就像當年的《笨小孩》，我一直希望可以做一首是像當年的笨小孩，有三個兄弟，用一首曲子表達一種正面的力量。
我們三個人的想法應該都是一樣的，就是希望在生命裏面很簡單，然後可以做一件事情，是讓我們三個人都覺得是很正面，然後很快樂的。
在這個打拼的路上，我們三個兄弟互相都看到彼此的辛苦，也看到彼此的堅持與執着。希望能用這種心境，去鼓勵所有不管是遇到困難、或者是遇到挫折的人。

想跟鴻升說的就是，這一趟太短了，下輩子我們再做朋友、我們再做兄弟，有你在身邊一起並肩作戰，是我這一輩子最驕傲最光榮的事。

竇智孔：
9月18日.晚上18:42分
在收到滾石發來的信息後，
我想這是你搞的鬼吧！
我崩潰了。
你..太賤了....
我會在我的隱形筆記本裡註記的。
然後，
我回頭翻著簡訊，
我找到了我們兄弟情開始的地方。
我承認我不是一個好相處的人。
但你的舉動讓我決定把牆全打開了。
簡訊裡
我：我們外景提來賓，不知道你會不會願意來幫忙。
你：只要你需要我的，我就盡全力幫忙，ok!（你就是這麼可愛）
我想緣分就是這麼簡單
然後，我們完成了一些回憶，
當然我們還有很多約好的計畫……

沒事，兄弟，再見。
兄弟我扛得住！
我們保持聯絡⋯。

⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯

『無論是逼不得已，或是因為是退卻而放棄、
無論如何，儘管緊緊擁抱遺憾，時間仍舊不可逆。
時針分針秒針，前進的頻率不同， 方向卻總是一致。
時針不會為了你而開始逆轉，但你可以順著時間的流，釐清造成的不甘的源頭，
毫無懸念的繼續順時針前行。』

—截自Alien黃鴻升，2019/11/28 寫於「Plan B」專輯概念

計劃趕不上變化、時間也無法倒轉，
面對遺憾和困難，請讓 扛得住 成為定番。

這是他留給地球的最後一首友情歌，只要有音樂陪伴，相信大家一定扛得住；願每個人都永遠記得鴻升帶來的美好，一起將他的正能量傳遞出去。

snippet.title: EVERGLOW (에버글로우) - LA DI DA MV
snippet.description:
♬ Available on iTunes, Apple Music : https://apple.co/3iSZ1iv
     Listen on Spotify : https://spoti.fi/32QJVVd


EVERGLOW (에버글로우) - LA DI DA MV 입니다.

#EVERGLOW #에버글로우 #LADIDA

‘독보적인 존재감’+‘강렬한 카리스마’로 돌아온 에버글로우
[-77.82X-78.29]로 전격 컴백!!

대체불가 퍼포먼스 장인 에버글로우가 한층 더 과감하고 폭발적인 그들만의 퍼포먼스로 돌아왔다.
- 글로벌 가요 시장이 주목하는 에버글로우!! 전 세계를 향해 외치는 에버글로우만의 메시지 ‘LA DI DA’
- 에버글로우만의 역대급 퍼포먼스와 강렬한 에너지 담은 타이틀곡 ‘LA DI DA’


독보적인 존재감 에버글로우 7개월 만에 컴백 ‘LA DI DA’

[ARRIVAL OF EVERGLOW], [HUSH], [reminiscence] 단 세 개의 앨범으로 전 세계 글로벌 팬들을 매료시킨 EVERGLOW가 두 번째 미니앨범 [-77.82X-78.29]와 함께 더욱 파워풀하고 강렬한 카리스마로 돌아왔다.

그 어느 때보다 독보적인 존재감을 발산하며 컴백하는 에버글로우의 이번 앨범 [-77.82X-78.29]는 그동안 에버글로우가 보여줬던 ‘강렬한 퍼포먼스’에서 한층 더 과감하고, 한 번도 시도해보지 않았던 퍼포먼스와 확장된 음악적 스펙트럼이 돋보이는 앨범이다. 그 누구도 대체할 수 없는 에버글로우만의 강렬한 에너지가 담겨있다.

이번 타이틀곡 ‘LA DI DA’는 Uptempo Electropop과 Retro의 컬래버레이션으로 신선한 레트로 댄스 감성을 극대화시키며 두 귀를 자극하는 곡이다. 현재의 어지러운 시대 속에서 잘난 척하며 불만에 가득 차 있는 HATER들을 향한 의미심장한 경고의 메시지가 함축적으로 담겨 있다. 에버글로우 멤버들의 새로운 목소리를 듣는 재미 또한 찾아볼 수 있는 곡이다. 수록곡들 역시 타이틀곡에 버금가는 퀄리티를 자랑한다.

또한 ‘LA DI DA’ 뮤직비디오는 현재의 어지러운 시대를 사이퍼 펑크라는 장르를 통해 적절하게 표현, 이 시대의 소외된 계층과 절망에 빠진 젊은 세대들을 위해 싸워나가며 그들을 위로하는 에버글로우의 모습을 강렬한 여전사로 표현했다.

E:U, 시현, 미아, 온다, 아샤, 이런 6인 6색의 다양한 매력으로 전 세계를 사로잡은 에버글로우는
지난 앨범 ‘DUN DUN’이 뮤직비디오 조회 수 1.5억을 돌파, ‘Adios’가 조회 수 1억을 돌파하며
K-pop을 책임지는 대세 글로벌 걸그룹으로서 확실히 자리매김했다.

이 기세에 힘입어 에버글로는 두 번째 미니앨범 [-77.82X-78.29]로 한 번 더 박차를 가하려고 한다. 전 세계가 에버글로우만의 퍼포먼스와 목소리에 눈과 귀가 매료될 시간이다.

snippet.localized.description:
♬ Available on iTunes, Apple Music : https://apple.co/3iSZ1iv
     Listen on Spotify : https://spoti.fi/32QJVVd


EVERGLOW (에버글로우) - LA DI DA MV 입니다.

#EVERGLOW #에버글로우 #LADIDA

‘독보적인 존재감’+‘강렬한 카리스마’로 돌아온 에버글로우
[-77.82X-78.29]로 전격 컴백!!

대체불가 퍼포먼스 장인 에버글로우가 한층 더 과감하고 폭발적인 그들만의 퍼포먼스로 돌아왔다.
- 글로벌 가요 시장이 주목하는 에버글로우!! 전 세계를 향해 외치는 에버글로우만의 메시지 ‘LA DI DA’
- 에버글로우만의 역대급 퍼포먼스와 강렬한 에너지 담은 타이틀곡 ‘LA DI DA’


독보적인 존재감 에버글로우 7개월 만에 컴백 ‘LA DI DA’

[ARRIVAL OF EVERGLOW], [HUSH], [reminiscence] 단 세 개의 앨범으로 전 세계 글로벌 팬들을 매료시킨 EVERGLOW가 두 번째 미니앨범 [-77.82X-78.29]와 함께 더욱 파워풀하고 강렬한 카리스마로 돌아왔다.

그 어느 때보다 독보적인 존재감을 발산하며 컴백하는 에버글로우의 이번 앨범 [-77.82X-78.29]는 그동안 에버글로우가 보여줬던 ‘강렬한 퍼포먼스’에서 한층 더 과감하고, 한 번도 시도해보지 않았던 퍼포먼스와 확장된 음악적 스펙트럼이 돋보이는 앨범이다. 그 누구도 대체할 수 없는 에버글로우만의 강렬한 에너지가 담겨있다.

이번 타이틀곡 ‘LA DI DA’는 Uptempo Electropop과 Retro의 컬래버레이션으로 신선한 레트로 댄스 감성을 극대화시키며 두 귀를 자극하는 곡이다. 현재의 어지러운 시대 속에서 잘난 척하며 불만에 가득 차 있는 HATER들을 향한 의미심장한 경고의 메시지가 함축적으로 담겨 있다. 에버글로우 멤버들의 새로운 목소리를 듣는 재미 또한 찾아볼 수 있는 곡이다. 수록곡들 역시 타이틀곡에 버금가는 퀄리티를 자랑한다.

또한 ‘LA DI DA’ 뮤직비디오는 현재의 어지러운 시대를 사이퍼 펑크라는 장르를 통해 적절하게 표현, 이 시대의 소외된 계층과 절망에 빠진 젊은 세대들을 위해 싸워나가며 그들을 위로하는 에버글로우의 모습을 강렬한 여전사로 표현했다.

E:U, 시현, 미아, 온다, 아샤, 이런 6인 6색의 다양한 매력으로 전 세계를 사로잡은 에버글로우는
지난 앨범 ‘DUN DUN’이 뮤직비디오 조회 수 1.5억을 돌파, ‘Adios’가 조회 수 1억을 돌파하며
K-pop을 책임지는 대세 글로벌 걸그룹으로서 확실히 자리매김했다.

이 기세에 힘입어 에버글로는 두 번째 미니앨범 [-77.82X-78.29]로 한 번 더 박차를 가하려고 한다. 전 세계가 에버글로우만의 퍼포먼스와 목소리에 눈과 귀가 매료될 시간이다.

snippet.title: 2020第55屆電視金鐘獎頒獎典禮 LIVE │ Vidol.tv
snippet.description:
「#第55屆電視金鐘獎」頒獎典禮於國父紀念館舉行，不同於以往，今年由三組藝人分別擔任三段主持工作，包含台劇人氣演員白家綺 GINO Tsaii 曾莞婷  陳冠霖牛仔部落格，影歌雙棲藝人
Lulu 黃路梓茵 搭配 盧廣仲及曾國城加炎亞綸 Aaron Yan 的組合，星光大道則由去年表現可圈可點的黃豪平搭檔李霈瑜 大霈 聯手主持。

典禮開場主題以「歡迎來到金鐘獎」破題，由樂團「魚丁糸」的鍵盤手龔鈺祺（阿龔）獨挑大梁擔任編曲、製作及鋼琴演奏，以及享譽國際的知名年輕指揮家吳曜宇，率領台北愛樂青年管弦樂團，帶給所有人最美好的音樂饗宴，把榮耀獻給金鐘55入圍者們。第二段演出歌舞「這是我的舞台」，身兼主持人及表演嘉賓的Lulu和盧廣仲在舞台上互尬魅力；壓軸演出「夢想就要起飛」特邀「嘻哈教主」大支與「視覺藝術家」陳怡潔合作演出，大支特別為此次金鐘典禮創作歌曲「對手」，期望眾人也能接收到歌曲想要傳達的訊息「努力把夢做大」。

金鐘獎官網所舉辦【愛的鼓勵．應援友你】全民拍手影像大募集，超過百位粉絲鼓掌影像成一大亮點，以實際行動傳遞溫暖給金鐘55所有入圍者。

鎖定直播看第一手訊息
電視金鐘獎得獎者即將公布！
下載55金鐘APP速看得獎名單

●Android： bit.ly/2ZkltX

snippet.title: 林俊傑 JJ Lin《交換餘生 No Turning Back》Official Music Video
snippet.description:
Starring 特邀演出 | 阮經天 / 林予晞

JJ林俊傑第14張專輯 首波前導單曲《交換餘生》
https://jjlin.lnk.to/NoTurningBackAY

儘管命運的曲折，為了所愛奮不顧身
願交換餘生，只求存在彼此一生。

無論身處任一時空，都要緊握著的手
願交換餘生，只求此刻還能相依相守。
交換餘生，是深深相愛的義無反顧。
有分合、有失去、有遺憾、有重新面對人生
蘊含著每份情感的託付。
＿

當情感驅動著生命中的所有，則足以撼動餘生的每一刻擁有。

餘生，代表著一切，代表著所有，也代表著那位所愛的人
交換，是不顧一切，能放棄所有，只求換回那位所愛的人

宇宙與生命之間運行的奧妙，看似遙不可及且虛幻，但當情感作為運行的動力時，一切將融為生命的每個瞬間，組成每一種可能。JJ充滿情感的旋律遇上易家揚的優美文字，化為一首令人動容的作品。歌曲一開始的信號音，宛如解鎖著另一個時空的密碼，而隨即而來的弦樂，就像瞬間掉進了另一個狀態，曲勢的轉換，與歌詞緊緊密合著，開啟了另一段並行的故事，同時存在、相互擁有。易家揚的歌詞，從平行時空作為開端，優美之中卻帶有一絲哀戚，當人與人之間的情感才是本質，一體兩面的故事情節，又將何去何從。
人總說完美的結局是不存在的，那麼無論故事盡頭是我，非我，反面的人生哭過笑過，會否活成另一個平行存在的時空？
＿

MV 特別邀請 金馬影帝 阮經天跨刀與實力派演員 林予晞共同飆戲，用一首歌的時間，從相遇相知到相守，將一段深刻情感用力愛一遍。JJ林俊傑以客串角色為自己的MV畫龍點睛，成為兩段故事的串點，而貓咪又扮演著什麼角色，處處充滿巧思。MV虛實之間的拿捏，故事情節又寫實又虛幻，為動容的歌曲添加一份奇幻感受。兩段看似併行又看似互相牽引的故事線，是交換、是交錯，開放式結局引人深思。

#交換餘生#林俊傑#JJLIN

＿
◼︎ 交換餘生
詞：易家揚 曲：林俊傑

孤單聽雨的貓往時間裂縫裡看到了我 
雷電交加之外的另一些我 
 
烏雲靜止以後 跳進平行時空
那些我 旅行中的妳我
回憶胡亂穿梭 墜落

交換餘生 是我 非我 苦與樂
陰天之後總有續命的晴空 
如果我們幾經轉折 結局一樣不動  
也才算無愧這分合
 
定位心海的錨讓時間停頓的像慢動作 
妳說命運很壞吧幸好有我 
 
如果沒有以後 如果平行失控
那些我 不同人生的我
會以什麼方式 哭過

交換餘生 是我 非我 苦與樂
陰天之後總有續命的晴空 
如果我們幾經轉折 結局一樣不動  
也才算無愧這分合

雲等風 人等夢 愛輾過時光等什麼
記不住 認不出 淚眼中誰一樣臉紅

等妳說 等我說 一等就是一個宇宙
日升換月落 真愛換寂寞


交換餘生 也許 忘了 第幾夢
那時我們身處第幾號時空 
因為我們手心緊握 記憶也能緊扣  
可不怕前方的蟲洞

愛是時間的古董
＿

詞 Lyrics：易家揚
曲 Composer：林俊傑 JJ LIN
製作人 PRODUCER：林俊傑 JJ LIN
配唱製作 VOCAL PRODUCTION：林俊傑 JJ LIN

Episode 144: Annu's Crazy Jokes
------------------------------------------------------
Kapil Sharma welcomes one of Bollywood’s most talented and famous artists Annu Kapoor. Annu Kapoor spills hilarious anecdotes from his past. Kapil indulges him in various questions while cracking hilarious jokes.

About The Kapil Sharma Show Season 2 : 
----------------------------------------------------------------
Kapil Sharma is back with a new 'Salah Center' (Consultancy Business) in a Mohollah with absurd characters. The wealthy milkman Bachcha Yadav (Kiku Sharda) with his wife Titli Yadav (Bharti Singh) and sister-in-law Bhoori (Sumona Singh) is the one who has rented out houses within the Mohollah and is Kapil Sharma's business partner. The neighbors in the Mohollah are also full of quirks and don't shy away from the antics. With celebrities gracing every episode, The Kapil Sharma Show promises fun-filled entertaining weekends.

snippet.title: Israel Adesanya vs Paulo Costa: Adesanya retains title with TKO win | UFC 253 Recap| CBS Sports HQ
snippet.description:
Israel Adesanya and Paulo Costa spent months trading verbal shots, but when it came time to step into the Octagon at UFC 253, the only meaningful blows that landed were those of middleweight champion. After spending a full round beating up Costa's lead leg, Adesanya finished the challenger with punches in the second round of the main event on Fight Island in Abu Dhabi.

snippet.title: Funniest Bondi Moments - Bondi Rescue Season 12
snippet.description:
The funniest and weirdest moments from Bondi Rescue Season 12.
SUBSCRIBE - http://bit.ly/subscribebondirescue
Buy Official Merch NOW - http://bit.ly/YTbondimerch

—

Bondi Rescue follows the work of the elite professional Lifeguards who patrol Australia’s busiest beach. This is Australia’s real life Baywatch! Taking the viewers on their journey through mass rescues, drownings, resuscitations, shark sightings, and all number of the weird wonderful and #funnymoments Bondi Beach dishes up. 

In #BondiRescue the audience sees the action through the eyes of real characters and lifeguards like Hoppo, Deano, Reidy, Jesse, Maxi, Whippet and Harries, as they catch thieves, perform CPR, make drug busts, break up fights, and even handle a navy bomb that washes ashore one afternoon. Every year throws up new and completely unexpected challenges, and how lifeguards adapt is what makes Bondi Rescue a show that’s about much more than swimmers being saved in the surf.

snippet.title: Americans have rejected 'horrific' treatment of Coney Barrett
snippet.description:
The Democrats and the Left in the US will look to “absolutely destroy” President Donald Trump’s Supreme Court nominee Amy Coney Barrett in the exact same way they destroyed Brett Kavanaugh, according to Sky News host James Morrow.

President Trump announced Justice Barrett as his nominee to replace deceased former associate justice Ruth Bader Ginsburg after she passed away two weeks ago after a long battle with cancer.

The President noted the passing of Justice Ruth Bader Ginsburg, describing the former Judge as a “true American legend” and a “legal giant”.

Mr Trump went on to introduce Ms Barrett saying, “today it is my honour to nominate one of our nation’s most brilliant and gifted legal minds to the supreme court”.

However, people have begun to ramp up the hate rhetoric against Trump’s nominee, specifically focussing on her conservative views, and her family.

Justice Barrett has seven children, two of which were adopted from Haiti sparking some to label her and her husband “white colonisers”.

Mr Morrow said the Democrats will “not be able to resist over playing their hand” which will drive middle America into the president’s hands.

“This should be the absolute American Dream. It’s everything that they (the Left) hate, this lovely happy successful interracial family,” he said.

“They are going to try and destroy this woman and middle America is going to look at it and say ‘guys what is your problem’”.

Sky News host Rowan Dean said it is going to be a “Trump landslide because the average American looks at this stuff and thinks it’s horrific”.

snippet.title: Boca A Boca S02E04 | GIULIA BE, FRED, MENOS É MAIS e mais!
snippet.description:
Último episódio do #BocaABocaS2 Find Your Balance acabou e nosso coração continua quentinho de tanto amor que levamos e recebemos ao longo dessa caminhada. O programa ao vivo da #BiancaAndrade, #BocaRosa, vai embora, mas volta em novembro!
E pra terminar no estilo tivemos a presença soltinha da @GIULIA BE falando sobre os próximos passos de sua carreira e cantando um acústico de Menina Solta pra gente.
Em seguida tivemos um papo diferente no Tabuleiro no qual Marcela McGowan inverteu tudo e entrevistou a mim e ao meu namorado Bruno Carneiro, o Fred do canal @Desimpedidos, pra sabermos mais sobre relacionamento livre.
Em seguida exibimos o resultado de um convite muito especial que recebi da Clau pra cantarmos juntas, e com isso vencer um medinho íntimo meu, foi lindo 💜
Daí partiu pro sambinha, pro pagode, pra raiz brasiliense do @Grupo Menos é Mais cantando pra gente aquela Recaída que a gente ama, e pra finalizar e me emocionar demais, Fatalmente.
Ajude o projeto social da CUFA Mães da Favela #cufacontraovirus
Doe em www.maesdafavela.com.br

___
Ficha Técnica

Coordenação Geral: Creative Lagoinha
Produção: Creative Lagoinha
Light Design: Creative Lagoinha
Palco e Estrutura: Lagoinha Niteroi 
Técnicos de audio: Guiarone Adão e João Ricardo Silva
Banda: Marcos Oliveira, Michel Bastos, André Lima e Matheus Charles.
___
Gabriela Rocha nasceu em São Paulo no ano de 1994. Aos 5 anos iniciou seu ministério na igreja que frequentava, quando aos 13 participou do programa Raul Gil, onde suas voz se propagou pela nação. A partir de então, a cantora se dedicou por completo ao chamado do Senhor e se tornar voz de Deus, levando os louvores e ministrações a todos os povos. Em 2012 Gabriela lançou seu primeiro álbum Jesus, em 2014 Pra Onde Iremos? e em 2016, um ano agitado, uma cantora realizou os lançamentos de SML, EP Gabriela Rocha e Até Transbordar (Ao Vivo) seu primeiro CD/DVD ao vivo. Seu segundo EP, Céu, foi lançado em 2017 e tornou-se repertório das igrejas brasileiras e internacionais. Em 2019 ela lançou o EP “Hosana” com canções como: Eu e o Rei (Ao Vivo), A Ele a Glória (Ao Vivo) e Diz. Seu último lançamento foi a canção Lugar Secreto (Español) que contou com a participação de Christine D'Clario e o EP “Juntos Em Adoração (Live 2020)”.

Ficha Técnica

Coordenação Geral: Creative Lagoinha
Produção: Creative Lagoinha
Light Design: Creative Lagoinha
Palco e Estrutura: Lagoinha Niteroi 
Técnicos de audio: Guiarone Adão e João Ricardo Silva
Banda: Marcos Oliveira, Michel Bastos, André Lima e Matheus Charles.
___
Gabriela Rocha nasceu em São Paulo no ano de 1994. Aos 5 anos iniciou seu ministério na igreja que frequentava, quando aos 13 participou do programa Raul Gil, onde suas voz se propagou pela nação. A partir de então, a cantora se dedicou por completo ao chamado do Senhor e se tornar voz de Deus, levando os louvores e ministrações a todos os povos. Em 2012 Gabriela lançou seu primeiro álbum Jesus, em 2014 Pra Onde Iremos? e em 2016, um ano agitado, uma cantora realizou os lançamentos de SML, EP Gabriela Rocha e Até Transbordar (Ao Vivo) seu primeiro CD/DVD ao vivo. Seu segundo EP, Céu, foi lançado em 2017 e tornou-se repertório das igrejas brasileiras e internacionais. Em 2019 ela lançou o EP “Hosana” com canções como: Eu e o Rei (Ao Vivo), A Ele a Glória (Ao Vivo) e Diz. Seu último lançamento foi a canção Lugar Secreto (Español) que contou com a participação de Christine D'Clario e o EP “Juntos Em Adoração (Live 2020)”.
___

snippet.title: O relacionamento acabou pq o Biel perdeu a memória? Como está o nosso casamento?
snippet.description:
Acesse o Ysos, o app de encontros que a gente mais gosta: http://bit.ly/tbysos

Nosso relacionamento mudou muito depois da perda de memória do Biel? Ele está bem? Nós continuamos saindo com outras pessoas ou estamos apenas os dois?

Veja mais vídeos sobre a perda de memória do Biel em: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLb6l4-i4l5-4vPibIAWMibJUu4xD7SUKT 

⚑ Se inscreve no canal: https://bit.ly/canaltuyebiel
⚑ Nosso podcast: https://bit.ly/tuyebielpodcast
⚑ Site oficial: http://www.tuyebiel.com.br

OUTROS VÍDEOS QUE VOCÊ DEVE ASSISTIR (sempre muda!)
► Reagindo a fotos antigas de casal - https://youtu.be/xOEro94jAyg
► Brigas no relacionamento - https://youtu.be/nx_eizZhkhU
► Sair da rotina sem dinheiro - https://youtu.be/iQecE3Z95dg
► Sinais de que ela está gostando - https://youtu.be/MfggQfoPIng

✪ Contato profissional: comercial@tuyebiel.com.br
→ Sugestões e dúvidas: contato@tuyebiel.com.br
→ Imprensa: https://bit.ly/imprensa-tuyebiel

✚ Faça o seu ensaio sensual ou de casal com a gente: contato@tuyebiel.com.br
Conheça mais do trabalho no insta @primeiroensaio

✱ Redes Sociais Tuy e Biel
• Instagram do casal: @tuyebiel
• Instagram Tuy: @tuypotasso
• Instagram Biel: @bielvaz_oficial
• Twitter: @tuyebiel
♡ Site oficial: http://www.tuyebiel.com.br

[PERGUNTAS FREQUENTES]

✺ Preciso de ajuda... Como posso falar com vocês?
Mensalmente abrimos algumas vagas de consultoria via skype. Para saber mais e entrar na fila de espera envie um email para contato@tuyebiel.com.br
Explique no email quais são os seus problemas e porque você precisa de uma consultoria nossa - avaliaremos o caso e te passaremos todas as instruções sobre como funciona.

Caso não queira uma consultoria, a forma mais fácil de entrar em contato é através do insta @tuyebiel - fique ligado na caixinha de perguntas que disponibilizamos nos stories.

✺ Como funciona o relacionamento de vocês? É aberto ou vocês são só amigos?
Nós estamos juntos desde jan/2012 e temos um relacionamento liberal desde o início, o que significa que ficamos com outras pessoas juntos. NÃO É um relacionamento aberto porque não ficamos com pessoas separados (salvo raras exceções que envolvem beijo na boca e é conversado anteriormente). Somos melhores amigos, mas também casados no papel, morando juntos e muito apaixonados.

→ Quer entender melhor como funciona o nosso relacionamento? Acesse nosso podcast que explica tintim por tintim e ainda te dá dicas caso você queira ter algo parecido: https://bit.ly/relacionamentotuyebiel

✺ Vocês sentem ciúmes?
Sim, às vezes, mas sabemos contornar muito bem quando isso acontece. Sempre que algo gera ciúme, nós conversamos para entender se é algo individual ou se realmente naquela situação fez algum sentido.

→ Acesse nossa playlist sobre ciúmes: https://bit.ly/ciumestuyebiel

Aviso para o Youtube: Nossos vídeos tratam principalmente de educação sexual e sexualidade sem tabus e visam ensinar sobre o tema de forma descontraída.

✺ Preciso de ajuda... Como posso falar com vocês?
Mensalmente abrimos algumas vagas de consultoria via skype. Para saber mais e entrar na fila de espera envie um email para contato@tuyebiel.com.br
Explique no email quais são os seus problemas e porque você precisa de uma consultoria nossa - avaliaremos o caso e te passaremos todas as instruções sobre como funciona.

Caso não queira uma consultoria, a forma mais fácil de entrar em contato é através do insta @tuyebiel - fique ligado na caixinha de perguntas que disponibilizamos nos stories.

✺ Como funciona o relacionamento de vocês? É aberto ou vocês são só amigos?
Nós estamos juntos desde jan/2012 e temos um relacionamento liberal desde o início, o que significa que ficamos com outras pessoas juntos. NÃO É um relacionamento aberto porque não ficamos com pessoas separados (salvo raras exceções que envolvem beijo na boca e é conversado anteriormente). Somos melhores amigos, mas também casados no papel, morando juntos e muito apaixonados.

→ Quer entender melhor como funciona o nosso relacionamento? Acesse nosso podcast que explica tintim por tintim e ainda te dá dicas caso você queira ter algo parecido: https://bit.ly/relacionamentotuyebiel

✺ Vocês sentem ciúmes?
Sim, às vezes, mas sabemos contornar muito bem quando isso acontece. Sempre que algo gera ciúme, nós conversamos para entender se é algo individual ou se realmente naquela situação fez algum sentido.

→ Acesse nossa playlist sobre ciúmes: https://bit.ly/ciumestuyebiel

Aviso para o Youtube: Nossos vídeos tratam principalmente de educação sexual e sexualidade sem tabus e visam ensinar sobre o tema de forma descontraída.

Time campeão paulista demonstrou futebol pobre diante de um adversário esfacelado. E depois das atitudes dos dirigentes rubro-negros que irritaram boa parte da torcida, os meninos com alguns titulares ao lado, encararam, e bem, o elenco alviverde inteiro.

Leia mais sobre o tema no Blog do Mauro Cezar no UOL Esporte:

Alguns cartolas envergonham o torcedor do Fla. Garotos devolveram o orgulho diante de um Palmeiras pífio e muito mal treinado

https://bit.ly/36b5cLh

Minha coluna na Gazeta do Povo
 
Flamengo, Palmeiras… cada um pensou em si, o coronavírus foi apenas pretexto

https://bit.ly/36fvUSS

snippet.title: Wegen Mike & Kim: Basti rastet aus!!!😲💥 | Berlin - Tag & Nacht #2288
snippet.description:
Basti will Kim den Umgang mit Mike verbieten. Aber die lässt sich nichts von ihrem Patenonkel sagen und stellt ihn vor der Schule bloß! Basti ist total sauer und macht Mike und Kim im LA14 eine Ansage. Dabei rastet er komplett aus!

Die gescriptete Reality-Soap „Berlin - Tag & Nacht“ zeigt die coolste WG Berlins, mit Themen wie  Freundschaft, Liebe,  Eifersucht, Affären, Glück, Freude und Leiden. Wie im echten Leben eben!
Alte wie neue WG-Bewohner, u. a. Ole, Joe, Peggy, Krätze, Schmidti, Eule, Basti Paula, Piet, Milla, Leon und viele weitere, zeigen dir ihr Leben in Berlin, der bunten Metropole Deutschlands. Sie nehmen dich mit in ihre Wohngemeinschaften, auf ihre Arbeitsplätze, in den Club Matrix, den Friseursalon „Schnitte“ sowie die Bar LA 14. Auch ein Tattoostudio und das Fitnessstudio Body Burn gehören zu den unterschiedlichen und wechselnden Handlungsorten der Serie. Die Großstadt-Soap „Berlin – Tag & Nacht“ ist nicht zuletzt deshalb so beliebt, weil sie die Bewohner der WGs im Ringen mit alltäglichen Problemen zeigt: Affäre und Eifersucht, Erfolgsdruck im Beruf sowie viele  zwischenmenschliche Konflikte. 

"Berlin - Tag & Nacht" läuft Montag bis Freitag um 19:05 Uhr bei RTLZWEI.

snippet.localized.title: Wegen Mike & Kim: Basti rastet aus!!!😲💥 | Berlin - Tag & Nacht #2288
snippet.localized.description:
Basti will Kim den Umgang mit Mike verbieten. Aber die lässt sich nichts von ihrem Patenonkel sagen und stellt ihn vor der Schule bloß! Basti ist total sauer und macht Mike und Kim im LA14 eine Ansage. Dabei rastet er komplett aus!

Die gescriptete Reality-Soap „Berlin - Tag & Nacht“ zeigt die coolste WG Berlins, mit Themen wie  Freundschaft, Liebe,  Eifersucht, Affären, Glück, Freude und Leiden. Wie im echten Leben eben!
Alte wie neue WG-Bewohner, u. a. Ole, Joe, Peggy, Krätze, Schmidti, Eule, Basti Paula, Piet, Milla, Leon und viele weitere, zeigen dir ihr Leben in Berlin, der bunten Metropole Deutschlands. Sie nehmen dich mit in ihre Wohngemeinschaften, auf ihre Arbeitsplätze, in den Club Matrix, den Friseursalon „Schnitte“ sowie die Bar LA 14. Auch ein Tattoostudio und das Fitnessstudio Body Burn gehören zu den unterschiedlichen und wechselnden Handlungsorten der Serie. Die Großstadt-Soap „Berlin – Tag & Nacht“ ist nicht zuletzt deshalb so beliebt, weil sie die Bewohner der WGs im Ringen mit alltäglichen Problemen zeigt: Affäre und Eifersucht, Erfolgsdruck im Beruf sowie viele  zwischenmenschliche Konflikte. 

"Berlin - Tag & Nacht" läuft Montag bis Freitag um 19:05 Uhr bei RTLZWEI.

snippet.title: Minecraft Live: Vote for the Moobloom!
snippet.description: Which mob do you want to see in Minecraft? Vote for the Moobloom if you feel like flowers and cows living as separate entities has gone on long enough! It’s time to combine them and luckily for us it turned out adorable. Please don’t ask about the Meowtree, sometimes the question isn’t ”can we” but ”should we, because the branches have claws, oh no the branches ARE claws”. In any case, if you are on Team Moobloom head over to Minecraft Live on October 3rd to cast your vote! Read more about the mob vote here: https://minecraft.net/article/minecraft-live-vote-for-next-mob

snippet.title: Paderborns wilde 5 Minuten! HSV gewinnt 7-Tore-Spektakel: Paderborn - HSV 3:4 | 2. Bundesliga | DAZN
snippet.description:
Nach dem Auftaktsieg gegen Düsseldorf legt der HSV beim Bundesligaabsteiger Paderborn gut los und geht durch Wintzheimer und Terodde mit 2:0 in Führung. Paderborn reichen allerdings fünf Minuten, um das Spiel zu drehen: In der 34., 36. und 38. Minute sorgen ein Tor von Srebny und ein Führich-Doppelpack für die 3:2-Führung. Hamburgers Terodde gleicht in der 56. Minute aus, ehe Aaron Hunt in der 82. Minute zum 4:3 stellt und damit alle Paderborner Siegesbemühungen zunichte macht. Am Ende entscheidet der HSV das Montagsspektakel für sich und gewinnt sein zweites Spiel in Folge.

DAZN bietet einen Gratismonat, kostet danach 11,99 EUR monatlich und kann jederzeit monatlich gekündigt werden.

Deswegen heißt es seit einigen Wochen: #WegMitTausendTeilen – eine Challenge, zu der eBay gerade aufruft. Was dahinter steckt, erfahrt ihr im Video. Alle aussortierten Dinge, die ich nicht mehr benötige, verkaufe ich bei eBay. Alles was nicht zum Verkauf geeignet ist, verschenke oder spende ich. Weggeschmissen wird nur, wenn es wirklich nicht anders geht. Wenn ihr selbst unbenötigte Dinge verkaufen möchtet, dann schaut mal bei eBay vorbei: https://ebay.to/2PsK2OW
